    "guid": "ac6940fb-aac6-4de8-b622-55a662e23658",
    "name": "Live Channels",
    "overview": "Build looping virtual TV channels that appear natively in Jellyfin's Live TV.",
    "description": "Live Channels lets administrators build looping virtual TV channels from genres and official ratings or from a hand-picked list of items. Each channel, its guide, and its stream are served in-process through Jellyfin's own Live TV, so the channels appear automatically with no tuner to add, no URLs to paste, and no exposed endpoints.",
    "imageUrl": "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/JPKribs/jellyfin-plugin-livechannels/master/Jellyfin.Plugin.LiveChannels/Assets/Logo.png",
    "owner": "JPKribs",
    "category": "LiveTV",
    "versions": [
      {
        "version": "10.11.6.0",
        "changelog": "## Features\r\n- Add a Sessions tab that lists every active stream with its channel, start time, run time, and live encode speed, and a button to stop it\r\n- Warm up the next item while the current one is still playing so per-item channels switch files without a gap\r\n- Cap how many channels stream at once so a client that never disconnects cannot pile up encoders and overload the server\r\n- Add a stream time limit that closes any channel left running too long as a backstop for clients that never send a stop\r\n- Organise the Settings tab into collapsible sections",
        "targetAbi": "10.11.9.0",
        "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/JPKribs/jellyfin-plugin-livechannels/releases/download/v10.11.6.0/jellyfin-plugin-livechannels-10.11.6.0.zip",
        "checksum": "92fd29b1b779c12b81884ce2f971c1d5",
        "timestamp": "2026-06-29T07:03:56Z"
      },
      {
        "version": "10.11.5.0",
        "changelog": "## Features\r\n- Give the Popular channel its own tab to set its name, icon, rating limit, subtitle rule, and loop behaviour\r\n- Build the Popular channel from your recent, top rated, and most watched movies and shows\r\n- Measure most watched across the whole server by combining every user's play counts\r\n- Choose a default language in Settings that decides when Forced subtitles burn in",
        "targetAbi": "10.11.9.0",
        "sourceUrl": "https://github.com/JPKribs/jellyfin-plugin-livechannels/releases/download/v10.11.5.0/jellyfin-plugin-livechannels-10.11.5.0.zip",
        "checksum": "6f1cdbb705de1b683d604598102af573",
        "timestamp": "2026-06-29T03:40:05Z"
      },
